# GAP 4: Abstract concepts without physical basis
# How to define "good", "bad", "true", "false" in purely Limn terms?
# "goo: wha you wan" - but this is circular
# "tru: wha rea bei" - but "rea" (real) needs definition

# GAP 5: Modal verbs (can, must, should, may)
